---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import ShadeFinderDemo from '../../components/ShadeFinderDemo.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Shade Finder | AI Beauty Stylist"
  description="通过 3 个问题进入 AI 唇色诊断流程，后续可继续接入自拍分析与真实 SKU 推荐。"
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container section-copy narrow">
      <span class="eyebrow">Micro-tool MVP</span>
      <h1>Which lipstick shade actually suits you?</h1>
      <p>
        这个页面是项目第一批 Product-Led SEO 微工具入口，当前已具备真实页面结构、交互流程和 mock diagnosis API，下一步可继续接入自拍上传与外部模型服务。
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
      <ShadeFinderDemo />
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
